flowchart LR
    A[Optimized PFAS geometry] --> B[KNF context K1: gas]
    A --> C[KNF context K2: water-enabled molecule]
    D[Optimized PFAS-slab interface geometry] --> E[KNF context K3: interface]

    B --> F[SNCI, SCDI, SCDI variance, f1..f9]
    C --> G[SNCI, SCDI, SCDI variance, f1..f9]
    E --> H[SNCI, SCDI, SCDI variance, f1..f9]

    F --> I[Delta X_W-G]
    G --> I
    F --> J[Delta X_I-G]
    H --> J
    G --> K[Delta X_I-W]
    H --> K

    L[xTB energies: E_slab, E_PFAS, E_interface] --> M[Delta E_ads]
    M --> N[Delta Delta E = E_parallel - E_perpendicular]
    I --> O[Banding and interpretation]
    J --> O
    K --> O
    N --> O
